actress.name: Go Minsi
actress.description: Go Min-si is a South Korean actress, model and director managed by Mystic Story Entertainment. She is known for her prominent roles in television series such as Love Alarm (2019–2021), Sweet Home (2020–2023), Youth of May (2021), as well as the films The Witch: Part 1, The Subversion (2018) and Smugglers (2023).
